## Secrets & local configuration
# appsettings.json itself is tracked as a template — keep real keys
# (Vast.ai tokens, ComfyUI endpoints, etc.) in the files below.
appsettings.*.json
!appsettings.Development.json.example
appsettings.local.json
secrets.json
*.secret
*.secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pfx
*.key
*.pem

## Project media
# Sample clips and upscaled renders are large binaries — keep them local.
videos/input/*
videos/output/*
!videos/**/.gitkeep

## Tooling noise
# Regenerated by the Azure Copilot/MCP extension in Visual Studio; unrelated to this project.
.github/copilot-instructions.md

